3UA.F.summary: Karnov Group AB (publ) provides information in the areas of legal, tax and accounting, environmental, and health and safety in Denmark and Sweden. The company principally offers its products in the form of digital, such as subscription based online solutions. It provides its products under the brands of Karnov, Norstedts Juridik, VJS, Notisum, Legal Cross Border, and Forlaget Andersen. The company also publishes and sells printed books and journals, as well as hosts legal training courses. It primarily serves law firms, tax and accounting firms, corporates, and the public sector. The company was founded in 1867 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.

8XA.F.summary: Actic Group AB (publ) operates health and fitness clubs in Sweden, Norway, Germany, and Austria. It offers gym and swim facilities, as well as access to fitness clubs, PTs, and group training. The company also provides energy bars and drinks, training clothes, and other miscellaneous training products through online web shop; and training packages for corporate customers' employees, as well as arranges education program for instructors. It operates 181 clubs; and serves 222,000 members. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Solna, Sweden.
